stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_parse_request: parse (start_slot, count, columns)
    q_parse_request --> q_compute_range: data_column_serve_range = [max(current_epoch - MIN_EPOCHS, FULU_FORK_EPOCH), current_epoch]
    q_compute_range --> q_check_range: requested range within data_column_serve_range
    q_check_range --> q_error_unavailable: range outside serve_range
    q_check_range --> q_init_iter: range within serve_range
    q_error_unavailable --> [*]: respond ResourceUnavailable(3)
    q_init_iter --> q_iter_slot: for slot in [start_slot, start_slot + count)
    q_iter_slot --> q_check_blob_block: slot has blob-carrying block
    q_check_blob_block --> q_skip_slot: no known data columns for slot
    q_check_blob_block --> q_iter_columns: block with data columns exists
    q_skip_slot --> q_iter_slot: next slot
    q_iter_columns --> q_verify_column: for column_index in columns (slot, column_index) order
    q_verify_column --> q_send_chunk: send DataColumnSidecar response_chunk
    q_send_chunk --> q_check_limit: count <= MAX_REQUEST_DATA_COLUMN_SIDECARS
    q_check_limit --> q_verify_column: more columns to send
    q_check_limit --> q_iter_slot: all columns for slot sent, next slot
    q_iter_slot --> q_check_fork_change: fork choice changed
    q_check_fork_change --> [*]: stop responding
    q_iter_slot --> [*]: all slots processed
